cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL 

The paper discusses a connectionist model based on artificial neural networks, which is a common topic in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), neural networks (cs.NE), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The model is also applied to image processing tasks, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
